name: ALPHABET ABCDEFGH
description: What would happen if we took the word ALPHABET and systematically removed one letter from the original word and replaced it with an actual alphabet letter that follows in sequence in subsequent layers down? So ALPHABET would become ABPHABET and then ABCHABET, and so on. What are left with or what we have created I should say is part of the alphabet made from the word ALPHABET. Can you tell that I've been focused on autological words, phrases, and all aspects of the visual? It just astounds me that any of this is even possible. Crazy as it seems, it does indeed exist...and so much more is out there to be discovered and uncovered.
